UAE Board::Financial Controller / Accountant
Financial Controller / Accountant Accounting and Finanace
A leading Total Facilities Management Company is looking for a Financial Controller / Accountant who would be an MBA / CA / CPA or equivalent, having minimum 5 years experience in a similar capacity and preferably in the facilities management industry. Candidates must have skills in financial management, planning, budgeting, strategy formulation and cash flow management as well as strong and effective leadership skills. The company offers a competitive salary package and career growth opportunities. Interested and qualified candidates may apply by submitting their CVs with a recent photo and details of salary expectation to hr.jobs152014@gmail.com latest by 22nd May 2014.
